### Flag A (APPROVED) — add `Assessment.positionsComputedAt DateTime?`
One additive nullable column (cp2 migration) to back the status endpoint
(max(positionsComputedAt) per subject + overall). computedAt is the
MATERIALIZATION stamp (score entry) — conflating would be wrong. No new table,
no RLS change, SD count stays 4.

### Flag B (APPROVED) — gate = owner/admin OR form-teacher-of-arm
(ClassArm.classTeacherId == caller, via getTeacherScope homeroom set). No admin
gradebook in Phase 2, so the form teacher's "Recompute positions" button (in
the teacher gradebook, SUBJECT-NARROWED) gives the trigger a UI home. Subject
teachers see positions read-only. Full arm pass (with classPosition) runs at
slice-6 report-card build or via direct admin API.

